ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 20th day of January, 2016, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
